What can be done with Text ?

• Parse Text
• Find / Extract relevant information from text
• Classify text documents
• Search for relevant text documents
• Sentiment analysis
• Topic modeling

Comparison Functions...

• s.startswith(t)
• s.endswith(t)
• t in s
• s.isupper() , s.islower() , s.istitle()
• s.isalpha() , s.isdigit() , s.isalnum()

String Operations

• s.split(t)
• s.splitlines()
• s.join(t)
• s.strip() , s.rstrip()-reverse
• s.find(t) , s.rfind(t)
• s.replace(u,v)

File Operations

• f = open(filename, mode)
• f.readline() , f.read() , f.read(n)
• for line in f : doSomething(line)
• f.seek(n)
• f.write(message)
• f.close()
• f.closed
